23. EDGE CASES (AGENT MUST HANDLE)
shop has no logo
shop has no cover image
shop has no collections
shop has no map link
shop has no WhatsApp number (hide cart order CTA)
shop has phone but no WhatsApp
item has no image
item unavailable but still visible
owner hits free plan item limit
owner tries direct API call beyond plan limit
slug collision
slug changed after QR generation
suspended shop accessed publicly
admin impersonation session expires or ends
category delete with existing items
collection delete with linked items
empty cart WhatsApp attempt
shop not published yet
multiple shops under same owner

24. RECOMMENDED DEFAULTS
Default country: India
Default currency: INR
Default business type during onboarding: Mixed
Default storefront language: English
Default plan on signup: Free
Default watermark: enabled on Free
Default item availability: available
Default shop status after creation: Draft

