26. FINAL IMPLEMENTATION DIRECTIVE
Definition of “MVP Complete”
The MVP is complete when:
An owner can sign up and publish a shop
The shop has categories, items, and collections
A customer can browse the public storefront
A customer can add items to cart and send via WhatsApp
The owner can download a QR for the storefront
Plan restrictions work
Paid analytics are visible
Super admin can manage shops and plans
Super admin can create shops on behalf of owners
Super admin impersonation is logged and functional
